09:51.323 --> 09:52.291
OK.

09:52.324 --> 09:54.425
Enlighten me.

09:54.459 --> 09:58.863
OK.

09:58.897 --> 10:01.967
I guess... I guess
the way I see it,

10:01.999 --> 10:03.434
