the morning, there's

10:03.468 --> 10:04.870
what I want to do that day.

10:04.902 --> 10:07.572
And there's what
life has in store.

10:07.605 --> 10:11.175
And the two hardly
ever seem to match up.

10:11.209 --> 10:14.112
I guess the one thing
you can really count on

10:14.145 --> 10:17.449
is that, you can't
count on anything.

10:17.482 --> 10:20.552
