have the same kind of effect

10:59.925 --> 11:02.261
on me.

11:02.294 --> 11:03.195
Fair enough.

11:17.642 --> 11:19.176
No, it was really fun for me.

11:19.209 --> 11:22.446
I just like being around
people and... yeah, I mean,

11:22.479 --> 11:23.581
I'm... heh-heh.

11:23.614 --> 11:25.182
I have no.

11:25.215 --> 11:26.118
Yeah.

11:26.151 --> 11:27.386
Yeah, we did.

11:27.419 --> 11:29.488
