be catching any monster trout.

13:14.425 --> 13:15.794
You'd be surprised.

13:15.826 --> 13:18.362
My dad caught a 2-foot
catfish right there.

13:18.396 --> 13:20.332
Are you serious?

13:20.364 --> 13:20.765
No.

13:20.799 --> 13:21.533
Jerk.

13:23.368 --> 13:25.804
We can go for a hike
instead if you want.

13:25.836 --> 13:27.138
No, I like it here.

13:27.171 --> 13:28.806
It's peaceful.

13:28.839 --> 13:30.776
Yeah, it is.

13:30.809 --> 13:33.178
You know, my dad, he
actually built the cabin.

13:33.210 --> 13:34.579
Cut the logs for
it and everything.

13:34.612 --> 13:37.049
That's impressive.

13:37.081 --> 13:39.383
I think your dad and my dad
would have gotten along really

13:39.416 --> 13:40.285
well.

13:42.420 --> 13:43.288
Yeah, probably.

13:50.295 --> 13:52.564
He has his own way of doing
things, John, you know?

13:52.597 --> 13:54.766
Yeah, he certainly does.

13:54.799 --> 13:56.401
Will you relax?

13:56.434 --> 13:58.136
He's hard on every guy I've
ever introduced him to.

13:58.169 --> 14:00.072
