15:10.941 --> 15:13.344
Tell me something, John.

15:13.377 --> 15:16.214
What kind of man are you?

15:16.247 --> 15:16.882
Sir?

15:16.915 --> 15:17.716
Come inside.

15:40.405 --> 15:43.208
