17:06.590 --> 17:07.925
Once you've collected
the money, you

17:07.959 --> 17:11.595
will call a man named David.

17:11.628 --> 17:13.498
Be careful with David.

17:13.530 --> 17:15.598
He is unstable, violent.

17:15.632 --> 17:18.269
Do not push him.

17:18.303 --> 17:21.906
Most importantly, David does
not know I have your wife.

17:21.939 --> 17:24.409
