you to the cabin.

17:24.441 --> 17:25.675
That's all he knows.

17:25.709 --> 17:27.945
He does what I tell him.

17:27.978 --> 17:30.015
Remember how much you
love your life, John.

17:30.047 --> 17:32.816
Remember how much
she means to you.

17:32.850 --> 17:35.420
