18:07.485 --> 18:08.086
You talked?

18:08.119 --> 18:08.853
He talked.

18:08.885 --> 18:10.454
I listened.

18:10.488 --> 18:14.426
Are you... you sure about this?

18:14.459 --> 18:15.826
Anne makes me...

18:20.898 --> 18:23.001
Yeah, I'm sure.

18:25.001 --> 18:29.873
