if it wasn't for you.

18:36.748 --> 18:42.953
So it seems fitting you
should be my best man, right?

18:44.956 --> 18:46.491
Yeah.

18:46.524 --> 18:47.825
Shit, yeah.

18:47.859 --> 18:49.828
Yeah, you got it, brother.

18:49.861 --> 18:50.795
Yeah.

18:50.827 --> 18:52.363
Come here, man.

18:52.396 --> 18:53.097
Come here.

18:56.167 --> 18:58.103
