23:57.301 --> 23:58.302
Hey.

23:58.334 --> 23:59.303
Sorry.

23:59.335 --> 24:00.837
Big day, right?

24:02.405 --> 24:04.975
The pastor says we're going
to start in about 20 or so.

24:05.008 --> 24:05.977
